name: Grogu, Eat!
description:
1. If the game exe does not load in the browser, then in order to play the game, please open start.html with Visual Studio Code, with the Live Server (Five Server) Visual Studio Code extension installed.  
  2. The goal of the game is to collect the correct frog to feed Grogu. One is the correct frog, the other is poisonous (the decoy). - This mechanic is currently bugged and not functioning correctly.
  3. Have fun feeding Grogu!
